Power BI
It is a business analytics tool developed by Microsoft that enables users to visualize and analyze data with greater speed, efficiency, and
understanding.
It offers interactive visualizations, business intelligence capabilities, and an easy-to-use interface for creating reports and dashboards.

#Components of Power BI
- Power BI Desktop
- Power BI Service
- Power BI Mobile Apps
- Power BI Report Server

#Key Features of Power BI
- Data Connectivity
- Data Transformation
- Visualization
- Dashboard and Reports
- DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)

#Benefits of using Power BI
- Ease of use
- Real-Time insight
- Colloboration and sharing 
- Cost-Effective
- Integeration with Other Tools

#Who can Benefits from Power BI
- Business analysts, data analysts, and data scientists
- Decision-makers and executive
- IT Professionals
